    <line>my grief</line>
    <line>allowed me no</line>
    <line>respite, <del rend="strikethrough">N</del></line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">No event of my</del></line>
    <line>No incident</line>
    <line>occurred from</line>
    <line>which my rage</line>
    <line>&amp; misery could</line>
    <line>not extract its</line>
    <line>food.</line>
